</td><td class=menuhead nowrap>April 17th, 2001</td></tr><tr><td class=menudata colspan=2>
<div id="main208" style="display:none;">
<br><ul>           Well we knew it couldn't have been true. When the servers came down            today for an emergency patch, Verant put a secondary patch message in            the clarified the spawn rate of Venril Sathir and his remains -          <blockquote> To clear up some confusion, we wanted to let everyone know            that we have changed the timing of the spawn of the Venril Sathir remains.            It no longer appears directly after the death of Venril Sathir. And            we also urge you to read the patch message below about the changes to            this creature. </blockquote>         Look at the bright side.. at least we don't have to deal with the Cazic          Skin anymore for our epic.          <p></p>         <br><br>-Graffe</ul></div>
